So we've all got standard-issue tongues, taste
buds, brains. Why does food taste differently

00:00:04.930 --> 00:00:06.870
to different people?

00:00:06.870 --> 00:00:13.870
Anthony here for Dnews. I am NOT hot sauce
fan and my dad loves. He puts that on everything.

