when we were hunter-gatherers, finding high-calorie

00:02:11.439 --> 00:02:13.629
food was important for survival.

00:02:13.629 --> 00:02:18.140
Bitter tastes signal poisonous plants like
that black licorice flavor.

00:02:18.140 --> 00:02:24.010
Salty foods have important minerals and vitamins.
So a super taster can find healthier foods

00:02:24.010 --> 00:02:26.590
and avoid dangerous ones more easily.

